[b]TVO - Allan Gregg in Conversation: Neil Postman - technology is no substitute for human values[/b]

Neil Postman offers a critique of our modern philosophical condition by challenging our widely held assumptions concerning education, technology and media. His new book is called &quot;Building a Bridge to the Nineteenth Century&quot;.  (Original broadcast 2000)

